'''荷里路德公園'''（{{lang-en|Holyrood Park}}）是[[英國|英國]][[蘇格蘭|蘇格蘭]]首都[[愛丁堡|愛丁堡]]市中心的一座皇家公園，位於[[愛丁堡城堡|愛丁堡城堡]]以東約1英里處。公園面積{{convert|650|acre|ha|adj=on}}，內部地形景觀多樣，和[[荷里路德宮|荷里路德宮]]鄰接<ref>{{cite web | url = http://canmore.rcahms.gov.uk/en/site/52219/details/edinburgh+holyrood+park+general+and+perimeter+wall/ | title = Edinburgh, Holyrood Park, General and Perimeter Wall | accessdate = 2010-09-15 | archive-date = 2012-08-18 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20120818184454/http://canmore.rcahms.gov.uk/en/site/52219/details/edinburgh+holyrood+park+general+and+perimeter+wall/ | dead-url = no }}</ref>。現在荷里路德公園對公眾開放。

